In integration projects, user stories are usually divided based on:
Interface/System
Functional Capability
API/Event Flow
Error Handling
Security
Monitoring
Reporting/Audit

###Interface	Story Type	Purpose
Frontend → SSO	Consent Capture	Capture customer consent
SSO → OneTrust	Authentication + Consent Validation	Validate user/token
OneTrust → IH	Consent Event Publishing	Publish consent updates
IH → CDP	Customer Profile Sync	Update customer profile
IH → SFMC	Marketing Consent Sync	Update subscriptions
IH → SFSC	Service Consent Sync	Update service visibility
IH → Regional Consent Service	Regional Rule Validation	Apply geography-specific rules
Monitoring Layer	Logging/Alerts	Operational monitoring
Audit Layer	Audit Storage	Compliance tracking
